<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Candidate Profile Updated - Review Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196f3 0%, #1976d2 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header .icon {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .alert-box {
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
      border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .info-box {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .info-row:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #666;
    }

    .info-value {
      color: #333;
    }

    .changes-box {
      background-color: #fff3e0;
      border: 2px solid #ff9800;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .changes-box h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #f57c00;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .field-list {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .field-list li {
      margin: 8px 0;
      color: #555;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196f3 0%, #1976d2 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #2196f3;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #2196f3;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ff9800;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">üîî</div>
      <h1>Candidate Profile Updated</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="alert-box">
        <p style="margin:0; font-size: 16px;">
          <strong>Action Required: Review Candidate Profile Update</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          A candidate has updated their profile and it requires your review and approval.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Candidate:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><strong>{{candidateName}}</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Event:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{eventTitle}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Updated At:</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{formatDateTime updatedAt}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Status:</span>
          <span class="info-value"><span class="badge">Pending Review</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if changedFieldsList}}
      <div class="changes-box">
        <h3>üìù Fields Changed:</h3>
        <ul class="field-list">
          {{#each changedFieldsList}}
          <li>{{this}}</li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
      {{else if changedFields}}
      <div class="changes-box">
        <h3>üìù Fields Changed:</h3>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">{{changedFields}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div style="background-color: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #f44336; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> The candidate's profile has been automatically unpublished and their status
          changed to "Profile Update Pending". They will not be visible to voters until you review and approve the
          changes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Please review the updated profile to ensure all information meets your event's standards and guidelines.
      </p>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="button">Review Profile Now</a>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>üí° Review Tip:</strong> Check that all updated information is accurate, appropriate, and follows your
          event guidelines. You can approve or reject the changes, or provide feedback to the candidate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">
        This is an automated notification from ITFY E-Voting Platform<br>
        <strong>Event Administration Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from <strong>ITFY E-Voting Platform</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{reviewUrl}}">Admin Dashboard</a> |
        <a href="mailto:support@itfy-evoting.com">Contact Support</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
        ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
